aa(lp377
VSo just to wrap up, I'd like to actually say that
p378
aVbeing able to work in this sort of field,
p379
aVall of us that work in this field
p380
aVthat's not only super-exciting science,
p381
aVbut also has the potential
p382
aVto impact on patients,
p383
